Package org.elasticsearch.xpack.sql.proto

Class ColumnInfo

java.lang.Object
org.elasticsearch.xpack.sql.proto.ColumnInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.elasticsearch.common.xcontent.ToXContent, org.elasticsearch.common.xcontent.ToXContentObject
public class ColumnInfo extends Object implements org.elasticsearch.common.xcontent.ToXContentObject
Information about a column returned with first query response. As this represents the response for all drivers, it is important for it to be explicit about its structure, in particular types (using es_type instead of DataType).
